body:
if the custom op is implemented in CUDA EP,  you must also register CUDA EP.
i.e. register both TensorRT EP and CUDA EP (in that order)

@jywu-msft How to register plugin op with Tensorrt?
I know how to register plugin op with CUDA and CPU, but as far as I know, onnxruntime can't support tensorrt plugin op, and can't register plugin op with Tensorrt provider.

> Dup of #7314 ? @jywu-msft @stevenlix any comments?

yes, it's a Dup question.

This issue has been automatically marked as stale due to inactivity and will be closed in 7 days if no further activity occurs. If further support is needed, please provide an update and/or more details.
